name: Art in the Open: A walk through The 606, Wicker Park, and Bucktown
description: There is art around every corner in Chicago's Wicker Park and Bucktown neighborhoods: public, private, and personal. If you're interested in seeing and thinking about the art around us, come along for a walk! We'll explore Chicago's newest park, the 606, and admire the murals in the neighborhoods. There are numerous options in the neighborhood for a post-walk beverage or snack.
